  <description>
    <p>DNSpect is a local-first DNS performance lab. It starts a localhost web UI, sends DNS queries to the resolvers you choose, and ranks the results with deterministic latency, failure-rate, and stability scoring.</p>
    <p>The app is designed for measurement integrity rather than resolver marketing. It keeps benchmark execution on your machine, exports CSV or JSON reports, and includes platform-aware DNS detection and guided apply instructions.</p>
  </description>
